  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "In terms of profitability, Apple's gross margin stood at 43.31% in fiscal year 2025, reflecting a slight improvement from 43.29% in fiscal year 2024 and 43.20% in fiscal year 2023. The operating margin was 30.29% in fiscal year 2025, up from 30.27% in fiscal year 2024 and 30.18% in fiscal year 2023. The net margin was 25.31% in fiscal year 2025, slightly higher than 25.29% in fiscal year 2024 and 25.20% in fiscal year 2023. These metrics suggest that Apple continues to maintain robust margins, indicating efficient cost management and pricing strategies.",
